channel.title: Is it weird that I have the same profile photo as another user in any website or social media page?
channel.description:
Yeah, and currently I consider that person my twin or that I'm his clone and I never even noticed it... Accidentally, I have the same profile photo as [url='https://forums.blackmesasource.com/index.php/User/57720-Nonimportantuser/']@Nonimportantuser[/url] and I really find it funny since I have a twin or master or whatever and I really think that would be a problem since he or all of you might mistook it a fabrication/plagiarism or what do you want to call it.
Could anyone share to me your experiences if you already had the same thing as mine?...
